OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of cloud and a few
OL,6,Fshowers will spread eastwards this
OL,7,Fmorning. Turning brighter behind with
OL,8,Fsome good spells of sunshine come the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling warm with lighter
OL,10,Fwinds than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA largely dry night with
OL,13,Fclear spells, possibly allowing a few
OL,14,Fmist patches to develop. Later in the
OL,15,Fnight some showery outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Flikely to arrive in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
