OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,6,Fbut rather cloudy with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain further west. The
OL,8,Fshowers becoming more widespread into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, and turning persistent
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowers
OL,13,For longer spells of rain likely
OL,14,Fthrough Sunday and into Monday,
OL,15,Fpossibly thundery. A few showers still
OL,16,Fpossible Tuesday. Temperatures
OL,17,Fgenerally returning closer to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
